definition: a soft blackish-brown resinous exudate from various rockroses used in perfumes especially as a fixative
details:
noun
- a soft blackish-brown resinous exudate from various rockroses used in perfumes especially as a fixative
= synonyms: ladanum
- a dark brown to greenish oleoresin that has a fragrant odor and is used as a fixative in perfumes
= synonyms: gum labdanum
